snippet.title: Johnny Depp Exposes Amber Heard For Lying About Charity Donations
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Exposes Amber Heard For Lying About Charity Donations
Subscribe Here ☛ http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/3qF38D7

A claim from Amber Heard that she would donate all of her divorce settlement with Johnny Depp to a charity is now being called into question. Depps legal team actually think that this could have even influenced the judges original decision in Depps libel trial. Now after visiting the court of appeals we have new evidence from Johnny Depp that suggests Amber Heard lied about the charity donations.
